<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<FrameLayout
    xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:background="#F1F6F9"
    tools:context=".fragments.lesson7.OverviewFragment">

    <androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView
        android:overScrollMode="never"
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent">
        <LinearLayout
            android:orientation="vertical"
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
            <LinearLayout
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="match_parent"
                android:orientation="vertical">
                <LinearLayout
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="20dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent"
                    android:orientation="vertical">
                    <TextView
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                        android:gravity="center_vertical"
                        android:text="Addition and Subtraction\nof Decimals"
                        android:textAppearance="@style/TextAppearance.AppCompat.Large"
                        android:textColor="@color/black" />
                    <Button
                        android:id="@+id/btn_tts"
                        android:text="Read Aloud"
                        android:layout_marginTop="5dp"
                        android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                        android:background="@drawable/btn_secondary_button"
                        android:drawableStart="@drawable/ic_text_to_speech"
                        android:textAllCaps="false"
                        android:drawablePadding="10dp"
                        android:paddingStart="10dp"
                        android:paddingEnd="20dp"
                        android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                        android:layout_height="48dp" />
                </LinearLayout>
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/description_1"
                    android:text="Decimals can be defined as a whole number; the fractional part is separated by a decimal point which can be read as “and”. The digits following the decimal point show a value smaller than one.\n\nPlace value is the value where a digit is in a decimal number.\n\nStandard form is the usual way to write a decimal, such as 7.32.\n\nWord form is writing the decimals in words, such as seven and one hundred twenty-five thousandths.\n\nLet’s study the table."
                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                <ImageView
                    android:id="@+id/example_1"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="400dp"
                    android:contentDescription="example"
                    android:layout_marginVertical="10dp"
                    android:src="@drawable/lesson_7_sample_1" />
                <TextView
                    android:id="@+id/description_2"
                    android:text="On the Place Value Chart\n\nBefore we proceed on addition and subtraction of decimals, it is necessary that you know how to read and write the standard form of the decimals. And now let’s try to work on to the next activities.\n\nActivity 1: Battle of Marathon\n\nRead the given figure and write its word name\n\nThe marathon is a long-distance race with an official distance of 42.1950 kilometers, usually run as a road race. The event was instituted in commemoration of the fabled run of the Greek soldier Pheidippides, a messenger from the Battle of Marathon to Athens, who reported the victory.\n\nActivity 2: Write the word name of the following decimal numbers:\n\n1. 6.4531 = ___________________________________________________________\n2. 7.96420 = __________________________________________________________\n3. 4.78012 = __________________________________________________________\n4. 57.8750 = __________________________________________________________\n5. 412.5632 =__________________________________________________________\n\nActivity 3: Write the standard form of the given word name\n\n1. Two and twenty-one thousand three hundred sixty-four ten thousandths = ____________________________\n2. Eight and four thousand seven hundred ninety-nine ten thousandths = ______________________________\n3. Three and eleven thousand five hundred one hundred thousandths = ________________________________\n3. Three and eleven thousand five hundred one hundred thousandths = ________________________________\n4. One hundred thirty-two and sixty-four ten thousandths = _____________________________\n5. Eighteen and three hundred seventeen ten thousandths = ____________________________"
                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                    android:textColor="@color/black"
                    android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                <ImageView
                    android:id="@+id/example_2"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="250dp"
                    android:contentDescription="example"
                    android:layout_marginVertical="10dp"
                    android:src="@drawable/lesson_7_sample_1_1" />
            </LinearLayout>

            <LinearLayout
                android:orientation="vertical"
                android:padding="16dp"
                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                    app:cardCornerRadius="16dp"
                    app:cardElevation="0dp"
                    app:cardBackgroundColor="#ffffff"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="match_parent">
                    <LinearLayout
                        android:orientation="vertical"
                        android:background="@drawable/bg_gradient_tutorial"
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent">
                        <TextView
                            android:text="Tutorial"
                            android:textSize="18sp"
                            android:paddingTop="10dp"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:textColor="@color/black"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                        <TextView
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:textColor="@color/black"
                            android:text="Are you struggling with the numbers mixing in your head? In this tutorial, we will guide you through the step-by-step process of this lesson!"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                        <Button
                            android:id="@+id/btn_tutorial"
                            android:text="Watch Tutorial"
                            android:textAllCaps="false"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                            android:textColor="@color/black"
                            android:background="@drawable/btn_secondary_button"
                            android:drawablePadding="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_width="150dp"
                            android:layout_height="48dp"/>
                    </LinearLayout>
                </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>
                <androidx.cardview.widget.CardView
                    app:cardCornerRadius="16dp"
                    app:cardElevation="0dp"
                    app:cardBackgroundColor="#ffffff"
                    android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                    android:layout_width="match_parent"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                    <LinearLayout
                        android:orientation="vertical"
                        android:background="@drawable/bg_gradient_quiz"
                        android:layout_width="match_parent"
                        android:layout_height="match_parent">
                        <TextView
                            android:text="Quiz"
                            android:textSize="18sp"
                            android:paddingTop="10dp"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:textColor="@color/white"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                        <LinearLayout
                            android:orientation="horizontal"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                            <ImageView
                                android:layout_gravity="center"
                                android:background="@drawable/bg_list"
                                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <LinearLayout
                                android:orientation="vertical"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="10"
                                    android:textSize="18sp"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="Multiple Choice Questions"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            </LinearLayout>
                        </LinearLayout>
                        <LinearLayout
                            android:orientation="horizontal"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                            <ImageView
                                android:layout_gravity="center"
                                android:background="@drawable/bg_clock"
                                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <LinearLayout
                                android:orientation="vertical"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="2 mins"
                                    android:textSize="18sp"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="Per Questions"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            </LinearLayout>
                        </LinearLayout>
                        <LinearLayout
                            android:orientation="horizontal"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                            <ImageView
                                android:layout_gravity="center"
                                android:background="@drawable/bg_trophy"
                                android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            <LinearLayout
                                android:orientation="vertical"
                                android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                                android:layout_width="match_parent"
                                android:layout_height="wrap_content">
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="50%"
                                    android:textSize="18sp"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_bold"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                                <TextView
                                    android:text="To Passed the Quiz"
                                    android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                                    android:textColor="@color/white"
                                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                            </LinearLayout>
                        </LinearLayout>
                        <TextView
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:text="Let's measure your problem-solving skills to assess your level of understanding."
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                            android:textColor="@color/white"
                            android:layout_width="match_parent"
                            android:layout_height="wrap_content"/>
                        <Button
                            android:id="@+id/btn_start_quiz"
                            android:text="Start Quiz!"
                            android:textAllCaps="false"
                            android:fontFamily="@font/geologica_regular"
                            android:textColor="@color/white"
                            android:background="@drawable/btn_primary_button"
                            android:drawablePadding="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
                            android:layout_marginBottom="16dp"
                            android:layout_marginHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:paddingHorizontal="16dp"
                            android:layout_width="150dp"
                            android:layout_height="48dp"/>
                    </LinearLayout>
                </androidx.cardview.widget.CardView>
            </LinearLayout>
        </LinearLayout>
    </androidx.core.widget.NestedScrollView>
</FrameLayout>